Don't drink on the job, don't do drugs.  Neither of these will solve any problems, nor provide a stable life for your child.  I don't know what industry you work in, but you run the risk of getting fired and losing everything you have worked for.<br>
<br>
Find other ways to deal with the stress.  Solve the problem, don't mask it with a superficial, temporary fix.  There are many proven methods to reduce or control stress out there, use one of them.<br>
